The paper also proposes a fully unsupervised method, which involves clustering and monitoring, indicating that machine learning techniques are used, hence cs.LG is also likely. Additionally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on three datasets, indicating that it involves multimedia analysis, hence cs.MM is also likely. The paper also involves the use of pseudo-labels, indicating that it involves artificial intelligence, hence cs.AI is also likely. Finally, the paper involves the use of sampling to promote convergence, indicating that it involves cryptography and security, hence cs.CR is also likely.
